Package com.example.drinks.CustomerData

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CustomerDAO
    CustomerDAO is an interface that is used by the CustomerDB class This is a DAO that is used to get the data from the database as well as insert new entries
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Customer
    Customer CLASS This class is in the database CustomerDB and is an Entity that is stored in it The Entity will auto Generate a Primary key so that it is Unique to each customer It will also store the Name of the customer and the Location where they are sitting
    CustomerDB
    An abstract class which stores the framework of the Database This Database stores the Customer Class as its entities
    CustomerListAdapter
    CustomerListAdapter is a class which used the RecyclerView class to display all of the Customers and the total amount that customer has spent when viewing
    CustomerListViewer
    A Class used to display the current View
